# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# CODEOWNERS — Mandatory reviewers for pull requests
#
# Format: <pattern> <@owner1> <@owner2>
# Owners listed here are REQUIRED to approve PRs touching matched files.
#
# Replace @your-org/your-team with your actual GitHub team or usernames.
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Default: require team review for all changes
*                           @your-org/platform-team

# Security-sensitive files: require security team review
.github/workflows/          @your-org/platform-team @your-org/security-team
.github/dependabot.yml      @your-org/platform-team @your-org/security-team
.pre-commit-config.yaml     @your-org/platform-team @your-org/security-team
.secrets.baseline           @your-org/security-team
requirements.txt            @your-org/platform-team

# Application source code
src/                        @your-org/platform-team
app.py                      @your-org/platform-team
